            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Ultima clauserunt Par<lb break="no" n="2"/>carum stamina filo <lb n="3"/>Principii miserandi diem <lb n="4"/>quem gloria nisi <lb n="5"/>avus adque pater puerum <lb n="6"/>dedere &amp;lt;p=R&amp;gt;raeclara <lb n="7"/>militia patruoque suo iun<lb break="no" n="8"/>xere fovendum <lb n="9"/>cum primum pulchra lanu<lb break="no" n="10"/>gine sumeret annos <lb n="11"/>spectantes magnum patri<lb break="no" n="12"/>ae columenque futurum <lb n="13"/>heu miseri gloriari sibi <lb n="14"/>laetamque senectam <lb n="15"/><expan><abbr>crudele</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> luctum domui <lb n="16"/>Ravenna remisit <lb n="17"/>hoc miseros titulo pro<lb break="no" n="18"/>prium signasse dolorem 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Hedera am Ende von Z. 4, 8 u. 12. (B): CLE: Z. 6: praeclara.</p>
            </div>
